 could Germany Win WWII?'  The idea is to explore an alternate history up to the present day... where would be technologically?  Would Germany and Japan become the world super powers and enter into a cold war?  Would that struggle lead to Germany expanding into manned space travel more rapidly than our history did?  <br>
